      },
      "rationale": "Stiffness characterises the load-sharing behaviour of the construct under physiological spinal loads. Yield force and force at 40 mm displacement are ASTM F1717 standard endpoints directly linked to fatigue life prediction and fracture risk. Clinical relevance is documented in the simulation plan with reference to FDA guidance on spinal implant V&V. Gradation 2 satisfied."
